      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1780110846911,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "3 pillars of LLM Observability\n\n1. Traces -> Where it trace each and every step (agent reasoning flow) -> Langsmith /langfuse -> Prompt -> Tool Call -> Observation -> Result\n2. Logs -> WHere it print the API success /failure calls, Exepction -> Normal logs/ Langfuse\n3. Metrics -> Aggreated Measurements -> Promethesus + grafana -> Avg Latency, Token Size, Cost, Error rate\n \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3 pillars of LLM Observability\n\n1. Traces -> Where it trace each and every step (agent reasoning flow) -> Langsmith /langfuse -> Prompt -> Tool Call -> Observation -> Result\n2. Logs -> WHere it print the API success /failure calls, Exepction -> Normal logs/ Langfuse\n3. Metrics -> Aggreated Measurements -> Promethesus + grafana -> Avg Latency, Token Size, Cost, Error rate\n \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
